%%{init: {'theme':'neutral', 'themeVariables': {'fontSize':'15px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant Svc as SplitwiseService
    participant F as SplitFactory
    participant St as SplitStrategy
    participant BS as BalanceSheet
    participant Obs as ExpenseObserver

    Client->>Svc: addExpense(group, payer, amount, type, input)
    Svc->>Svc: validate group, payer, participants, amount
    Svc->>F: create(type)
    F-->>Svc: SplitStrategy
    Svc->>St: computeShares(totalCents, input)
    Note over St: shares sum EXACTLY to total<br/>(leftover cents distributed deterministically)
    St-->>Svc: {participant → cents}

    loop each participant (payer owes nothing)
        Svc->>BS: record(participant, payer, share)
        Note over BS: atomic merge on one PairKey<br/>— lock-free, self-balancing
    end

    Svc->>Svc: build Expense, append to group history
    Svc->>Obs: onExpenseAdded(expense)
    Svc-->>Client: Expense
